member.name: P:Google.Apis.Dfareporting.v1_2.Data.Report.ScheduleData.RunsOnDayOfMonth
member.summary: Enum to define for "MONTHLY" scheduled reports whether reports should be repeated on the same day of the month as "startDate" or the same day of the week of the month.
